====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# {{lb|zh|literary}} to be able to
#: {{zh-co|克勤克儉|hardworking and thrifty}}
#* {{zh-x|靡 不 有 初，鮮{xiǎn} 克 有 終。|All are [good] at first,<br/>But few prove themselves to be so at the last.|ref=Shijing}}
# to [[defeat]]; to [[vanquish]]; to [[conquer]]
#: {{syn|zh|剋//|戰勝}}
#: {{zh-co|克敵|to '''defeat''' the enemy}}
#* {{zh-x|^夏，五月，^鄭 ^伯 克 ^段 于 ^鄢。|In summer, in the fifth month, the {{w|Duke Zhuang of Zheng|Liege of Zheng}} '''overcame'''<!--穀梁傳 gives an interpretation of this passage in which 克 is said to mean 能, meaning 能殺. That interpretation may be consistent with the "overcome" understanding of 克 or it may be a separate definition.--> {{w|:zh:共叔段|Duan (Gongshu Duan)}} at [[Yanling|Yan]].|ref=Zuozhuan-D}}
# to [[subdue]]; to [[restrain]]
#: {{zh-co|克制|to restrain}}
#* {{zh-x|克己復禮 為{wéi} 仁。一日 克己復禮，天下 歸 仁 焉。|To '''subdue''' one's self and return to propriety, is perfect virtue. If a man can for one day '''subdue''' himself and return to propriety, all under heaven will ascribe perfect virtue to him.|ref=Analects}}
# to [[digest]]
#: {{zh-co|克食|to aid digestion}}
# to [[set]] (a time limit)
#: {{zh-co|克日|to '''set''' a date}}
# {{lb|zh|dialectal}} {{zh-pronunciation spelling of|去|tr=-}}<!--https://www.zhihu.com/question/19727884-->
#: {{zh-x|滾 出去\出克|to go away}}
